      "description": "## Create a brand\n\n> You should be logged into the Okta Admin Console as your Super Admin account.\n\n1. From the Okta Admin Console, go to **Customizations** > **Brands**.\n2. Select the **+ Create brand** button.\n3. Name your brand **Okta Ice** and select the **Create brand** button."
