      "description": "## Customize your theme\n\n1. Select **Okta Ice** from your list of brands. \n>Notice you're now on the Theme tab, where you can customize your brand's theme.\n2. Download the following images: \n    - https://cdn.auth0.com/website/okta-learning/labs/ice-logo.png\n    - https://cdn.auth0.com/website/okta-learning/labs/favicon.png\n    - https://cdn.auth0.com/website/okta-learning/labs/ice-cream-bg.png\n3. Update the **Logo** to ice-logo.png.\n4. Update the **Background** to ice-cream-bg.png.\n5. Update the **Favicon** to favicon.png.\n6. Update the Primary color to `#2d75bb`.\n7. Update the Secondary color to `#c7e5f5`.\n8. Select the **Save** button."
