      "description": "## Preview themes\n\nYou can preview the look and feel of Okta pages and from the Themes tab. By default, the Sign-in page preview is shown.\n\n1. Use the dropdown menu to select other preview options such as **Error pages** and **Emails**.\n2. Switch back to **Sign-in page** and select **Customize**.\n\n>This is where you can toggle on the Code editor for advanced customizations. However, this requires setting up a custom domain that you have ownership of."
